01:17:26,610 --> 01:17:34,150
 ♫ When darkness falls in my quiet heart ♫ 

1003
01:17:34,150 --> 01:17:40,750
 ♫ Outside is filled with so many stars ♫ 

1004
01:17:40,750 --> 01:17:44,200
 ♫ You, who loved purple ♫ 

1005
01:17:44,200 --> 01:17:47,130
 Weren't you going to meet and tell him, anyway? 

1006
01:17:47,130 --> 01:17:51,340
 Yeah. But telling him myself and getting
caught are two different things. 

1007
01:17:51,340 --> 01:17:52,550
 It doesn't matter to me. 

1008
01:17:52,550 --> 01:17:55,040
 It matters to me. Don't come back here. 

1009
01:17:55,040 --> 01:17:56,430
 Let me ask you something. 

1010
01:17:56,430 --> 01:17:58,620
 Is there an attendant
by the name of Seo Jong Yeon? 

1011
01:17:58,620 --> 01:18:02,380
 Some strange guy was looking for Seo Jong Yeon. 

1012
01:18:02,380 --> 01:18:03,970
 What's going on, Jong Hui? 

1013
01:18:03,970 --> 01:18:07,140
 - I have to run away. As soon as possible!
- Stop! 

1014
01:18:07,140 --> 01:18:09,080
 Can't you just leave me alone? 

1015
01:18:09,080 --> 01:18:12,280
 I'm utterly humiliated because
my lowest has been exposed. 

1016
01:18:12,280 --> 01:18:13,350
 Let go. Let go! 

1017
01:18:13,350 --> 01:18:15,850
 Let me stay by your side even as a friend. 

1018
